text: S達o Vicente is an island of Cape Verde. It is in the Barlavento Islands group. S達o Vicente was discovered by the Portuguese discoverer Diogo Afonso on 22 January 1462. 92% of the island population lives in the urban area of Mindelo.2010 Census Summary It is on the Porto Grande Bay. Mindelo is the capital city of the municipality. S達o Vicente has a hot and dry climate.
